reviewText: These are excellent videos detailing the before and after lives of the characters from Lonesome Dove. In the Streets of Laredo a very excellent story, I think Capt. Call played by James Garner was not his "Cup of Tea."  He's a great actor but I think he has been miscast for this part, it's hard to top Tommy Lee Jones or Jon Vaught for the Woodrow F. Call charater.  Don't let this little bit of negativism put you off from these two excellent Videos.
